---
title: Spanakopita-Inspired Beef Patties with Greek Lemon Potatoes
description: Tender, lemony potatoes and a crunchy salad are the perfect accompaniment to these feta and spinach-infused beef patties. This meal will make you feel like you're on a Greek island, basking in the sun, no matter what time of year!

