garlic, onion and parsley) (barley, milk, oats, rye, sesame, soy, wheat) • Dill • Zesty garlic blend (granulated garlic, cornmeal, salt, dehydrated red bell pepper flakes, spices, sugar, herbs, canola oil, silicon dioxide, citric acid) (sulphites) • Garlic.
